{"about_the_game":"In a bleak, industrial future, you awaken to a world dominated by soulless machinery rusting under poisoned skies. The people around you, lifeless and oblivious, are blind to the rot that has overtaken their existence. But you are different\u2014haunted by a fleeting vision of a world before: an ocean, blue and beautiful beneath a moonlit sky. Driven by that memory, you must navigate this twisted landscape in search of what is real. They sense your difference and watch your every move. Find what lies beyond these rusted walls before they find you. This is your <strong>Rusted Awakening!</strong><br><br>What to expect in <strong>Rusted Awakening?</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874490/extras/BRUTAL.png?t=1737911079\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874490/extras/Movie_065-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1737911079\" /><i>Combat is brutal and every shot counts. There is no mercy here. Do what you must.</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874490/extras/DARK.png?t=1737911079\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874490/extras/Movie_071-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1737911079\" /><i>Dark horrors lie in wait for you, but know that beyond there may still be a light.</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874490/extras/SURREAL.png?t=1737911079\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874490/extras/Movie_038-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1737911079\" /><i>Walls shift, floors collapse, traps spring at every corner, and secrets wait to be uncovered.</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874490/extras/INTRO40.png?t=173791